1
00:01:42,640 --> 00:01:43,239
Zhou Wan,

2
00:01:50,040 --> 00:01:50,799
do you

3
00:01:52,680 --> 00:01:53,760
have to work for Lan Yue?

4
00:01:58,159 --> 00:01:59,079
I have my reasons.

5
00:02:02,000 --> 00:02:02,599
Sorry,

6
00:02:02,920 --> 00:02:03,680
you haven't eaten

7
00:02:03,680 --> 00:02:04,680
since this morning.

8
00:02:05,120 --> 00:02:06,280
How about having dinner together?

9
00:02:07,640 --> 00:02:08,599
If you park here,

10
00:02:08,599 --> 00:02:09,960
the traffic police will drag your car away.

11
00:02:10,120 --> 00:02:11,159
It's late.

12
00:02:11,159 --> 00:02:12,120
You should go home.

13
00:02:46,960 --> 00:02:47,840
Where did you go?

14
00:02:51,520 --> 00:02:52,400
To see your boyfriend?

15
00:02:55,400 --> 00:02:56,560
Don't lie to me.

16
00:02:57,879 --> 00:02:58,520
What did you do?

17
00:02:59,560 --> 00:03:00,240
Jiang Yan and I

18
00:03:00,240 --> 00:03:01,439
went to visit his mom.

19
00:03:01,759 --> 00:03:02,680
I didn't tell you the details

20
00:03:02,680 --> 00:03:03,840
because I didn't want you to overthink.

21
00:03:04,080 --> 00:03:05,520
You're afraid I'll overthink.

22
00:03:06,759 --> 00:03:07,520
You're not overthinking.

23
00:03:08,199 --> 00:03:08,840
Do I look like

24
00:03:08,840 --> 00:03:09,840
I'm overthinking?

25
00:03:10,199 --> 00:03:10,599
You're not overthinking.

26
00:03:10,599 --> 00:03:11,400
How did you get here?

27
00:03:13,520 --> 00:03:14,439
I passed by.

28
00:03:14,560 --> 00:03:15,159
Are you stalking me?

29
00:03:15,280 --> 00:03:15,919
I passed by.

30
00:03:15,960 --> 00:03:16,479
Are you stalking me?

31
00:03:16,479 --> 00:03:17,319
I just passed by.

32
00:03:17,800 --> 00:03:18,439
You're stalking me.

33
00:03:25,240 --> 00:03:26,159
According to our agreement,

34
00:03:26,159 --> 00:03:26,840
I just promised

35
00:03:26,840 --> 00:03:28,039
to take care of your life,

36
00:03:28,039 --> 00:03:29,520
but it doesn't mean I have no freedom.

37
00:03:29,639 --> 00:03:30,280
Who I want to see,

38
00:03:30,280 --> 00:03:31,080
what I want to do,

39
00:03:31,120 --> 00:03:31,960
are all my freedom.

40
00:03:32,120 --> 00:03:33,240
What do you mean by your freedom?

41
00:03:34,000 --> 00:03:35,000
Isn't this your job?

42
00:03:36,479 --> 00:03:37,639
I sent you a bunch of messages,

43
00:03:37,639 --> 00:03:38,800
asking you what brand of soy sauce to buy,

44
00:03:38,800 --> 00:03:39,319
what vegetables to get,

45
00:03:39,319 --> 00:03:39,960
and what kind of eggs to pick,

46
00:03:39,960 --> 00:03:40,960
organic or not.

47
00:03:41,599 --> 00:03:42,840
How would I know the difference?

48
00:03:43,039 --> 00:03:44,120
You didn't reply to a single one of them.

49
00:03:44,280 --> 00:03:45,199
I did reply.

50
00:03:45,199 --> 00:03:45,680
Where?

51
00:03:45,680 --> 00:03:46,360
Check your phone and see if you replied.

52
00:03:46,360 --> 00:03:47,840
I just didn't reply about the eggs.

53
00:03:48,240 --> 00:03:49,360
That's because you're already 28.

54
00:03:49,360 --> 00:03:50,479
You're an adult now.

55
00:03:50,479 --> 00:03:51,000
You actually don't know

56
00:03:51,000 --> 00:03:51,879
what eggs to buy.

57
00:03:52,080 --> 00:03:52,840
It's none of your business whether I know

58
00:03:52,840 --> 00:03:53,400
what eggs to buy.

59
00:03:53,400 --> 00:03:54,599
If I ask, you have to answer me.

60
00:03:58,599 --> 00:03:59,840
Do you think you're the boss?

61
00:04:03,120 --> 00:04:03,680
Take it.

62
00:04:06,919 --> 00:04:08,919
Help me carry one, this is heavy.

63
00:04:11,520 --> 00:04:13,319
Are you being unreasonable?

64
00:05:13,759 --> 00:05:15,439
Now you can sleep well.

65
00:05:20,680 --> 00:05:21,879
You can sleep well like this?

66
00:05:31,360 --> 00:05:31,879
Don't move.

67
00:05:38,160 --> 00:05:39,480
I can't sleep like this.

68
00:05:39,600 --> 00:05:40,759
I don't care if you can sleep or not.

69
00:05:42,480 --> 00:05:43,439
As long as I can sleep, it's fine.

70
00:06:10,079 --> 00:06:10,959
Sister Zhou Wan.

71
00:06:11,279 --> 00:06:12,720
Someone sent you flowers again.

72
00:06:14,120 --> 00:06:15,199
Sister Wan.

73
00:06:16,199 --> 00:06:17,160
Who is it this time?

74
00:06:18,800 --> 00:06:19,480
Xin'er.

75
00:06:19,879 --> 00:06:20,759
I have another task.

76
00:06:21,279 --> 00:06:22,240
Could you go to

77
00:06:23,040 --> 00:06:24,920
the Engineering Archive Room of Lan Yue headquarters

78
00:06:25,040 --> 00:06:26,399
and get all the information

79
00:06:26,399 --> 00:06:27,040
of Phase I?

80
00:06:27,040 --> 00:06:27,839
The more detailed, the better.

81
00:06:27,839 --> 00:06:28,639
Because I want to see

82
00:06:28,639 --> 00:06:29,279
if there is anything

83
00:06:29,279 --> 00:06:30,240
we can learn from Phase II.

84
00:06:30,240 --> 00:06:31,199
Okay, I'll go right now.

85
00:06:39,000 --> 00:06:40,439
Hello, Miss Zhou.

86
00:06:40,920 --> 00:06:42,199
Did you see my flowers?

87
00:06:42,800 --> 00:06:44,079
Mr. Huang, thank you.

88
00:06:45,480 --> 00:06:46,800
I told you last time

89
00:06:46,920 --> 00:06:47,959
that you didn't have to spend so much.

90
00:06:48,040 --> 00:06:49,360
Since I met you

91
00:06:49,360 --> 00:06:50,399
last time,

92
00:06:50,720 --> 00:06:51,879
I truly believe

93
00:06:52,160 --> 00:06:53,920
flowers must be matched with a beauty.

94
00:06:55,879 --> 00:06:56,759
Mr. Huang, you also

95
00:06:56,759 --> 00:06:57,720
learned about

96
00:06:57,720 --> 00:06:58,519
our project.

97
00:06:58,759 --> 00:06:59,920
I'll come to your company

98
00:06:59,920 --> 00:07:00,639
as scheduled

99
00:07:00,639 --> 00:07:01,680
to discuss it in detail

100
00:07:01,680 --> 00:07:03,040
and match the demands of both sides.

101
00:07:03,560 --> 00:07:04,360
Is that okay?

102
00:07:05,399 --> 00:07:06,040
Miss Zhou,

103
00:07:06,399 --> 00:07:07,839
I was just about to talk to you about this.

104
00:07:08,360 --> 00:07:09,720
I have an emergency this afternoon,

105
00:07:09,720 --> 00:07:10,600
and I need to go on a business trip.

106
00:07:10,959 --> 00:07:11,680
So,

107
00:07:11,839 --> 00:07:12,480
I have to rush to

108
00:07:12,480 --> 00:07:13,879
the club in the suburbs to prepare.

109
00:07:14,560 --> 00:07:16,079
If it's convenient for you,

110
00:07:16,279 --> 00:07:17,360
can you come to the club

111
00:07:17,360 --> 00:07:18,040
to talk face to face?

112
00:07:19,519 --> 00:07:20,480
Or

113
00:07:20,480 --> 00:07:22,360
we can make an appointment

114
00:07:22,560 --> 00:07:23,399
when you come back.

115
00:07:25,000 --> 00:07:26,920
I will be away for a long time.

116
00:07:27,519 --> 00:07:29,600
If you really want to talk,

117
00:07:30,000 --> 00:07:31,040
I can only squeeze out some time

118
00:07:31,040 --> 00:07:32,160
in the afternoon.

119
00:07:32,560 --> 00:07:33,600
I'll send you the address.

120
00:07:34,600 --> 00:07:35,199
Hello.

121
00:07:44,160 --> 00:07:44,800
Please come in.

122
00:07:50,480 --> 00:07:51,040
Mr. Huang,

123
00:07:51,199 --> 00:07:52,360
Miss Zhou from Lan Yue is here.

124
00:07:54,839 --> 00:07:55,560
Let her in.

125
00:07:55,800 --> 00:07:56,360
Okay.

126
00:07:57,439 --> 00:07:58,480
Miss Zhou, please come in.

127
00:07:58,639 --> 00:07:59,480
Mr. Huang is inside.

128
00:08:04,600 --> 00:08:05,480
Mr. Huang, hello.

129
00:08:08,480 --> 00:08:09,360
I'm sorry

130
00:08:09,720 --> 00:08:11,160
to make you come all this way.

131
00:08:11,800 --> 00:08:13,040
I really had no choice.

132
00:08:13,360 --> 00:08:14,800
I have a last-minute business trip this afternoon,

133
00:08:15,079 --> 00:08:15,839
so I need to

134
00:08:15,959 --> 00:08:17,560
get these things ready quickly.

135
00:08:19,600 --> 00:08:20,079
Have a seat.

136
00:08:23,199 --> 00:08:24,079
Mr. Huang, you're too kind.

137
00:08:24,839 --> 00:08:25,519
This is the cooperation framework

138
00:08:25,519 --> 00:08:26,360
based on

139
00:08:26,360 --> 00:08:27,680
our previous communication.

140
00:08:28,240 --> 00:08:29,240
You can take a look.

141
00:08:29,600 --> 00:08:30,319
If there's anything...

142
00:08:30,519 --> 00:08:31,439
Look how busy I am.

143
00:08:32,159 --> 00:08:33,200
I forgot to ask Miss Zhou

144
00:08:33,200 --> 00:08:34,200
what you would like to drink.

145
00:08:34,720 --> 00:08:35,279
Coffee,

146
00:08:35,759 --> 00:08:36,399
soft drink,

147
00:08:37,480 --> 00:08:38,399
or

148
00:08:39,320 --> 00:08:40,080
some alcohol?

149
00:08:40,639 --> 00:08:42,399
You're welcome. I'm not thirsty.

150
00:08:46,039 --> 00:08:46,799
I'm allergic to alcohol.

151
00:08:50,480 --> 00:08:51,039
Okay.

152
00:08:55,360 --> 00:08:56,759
You are so young

153
00:08:57,120 --> 00:08:59,000
and have become the deputy director.

154
00:08:59,799 --> 00:09:02,159
I think you must be very smart

155
00:09:02,679 --> 00:09:04,440
and have some tricks.

156
00:09:05,519 --> 00:09:06,200
I'm glad

157
00:09:06,600 --> 00:09:07,480
to have

158
00:09:08,360 --> 00:09:09,639
the chance to see it today.

159
00:09:12,279 --> 00:09:13,720
Look, the wine is spilled on you.

160
00:09:13,840 --> 00:09:14,840
Let me help you wipe it off.

161
00:09:15,039 --> 00:09:15,679
I have a spare shirt for you.

162
00:09:15,679 --> 00:09:16,399
I'm sorry, okay?

163
00:09:16,399 --> 00:09:17,519
We can't continue today.

164
00:09:18,120 --> 00:09:18,919
Stop pretending.

165
00:09:18,919 --> 00:09:19,679
Let go of me.

166
00:09:29,200 --> 00:09:30,360
Try to touch me again.

167
00:09:31,679 --> 00:09:32,480
Are you crazy?

168
00:09:32,480 --> 00:09:33,360
How dare you spray me?

169
00:09:33,840 --> 00:09:34,759
Don't you want to

170
00:09:34,759 --> 00:09:35,360
work with our company?

171
00:09:41,039 --> 00:09:42,200
I won't let you off the hook.

172
00:09:46,480 --> 00:09:47,600
Okay, that's enough.

173
00:09:48,639 --> 00:09:49,399
That's amazing.

174
00:09:49,399 --> 00:09:50,519
Let me see

175
00:09:50,519 --> 00:09:51,240
what's wrong with your clothes.

176
00:09:52,159 --> 00:09:53,919
Let me tidy it up for you.

177
00:09:54,720 --> 00:09:55,279
My car broke down.

178
00:09:55,279 --> 00:09:56,399
Can you come and fix it, boss?

179
00:09:56,399 --> 00:09:57,159
Not today.

180
00:09:57,279 --> 00:09:58,440
Don't you see I'm dealing with the kid?

181
00:10:01,919 --> 00:10:02,960
Look who's here.

182
00:10:02,960 --> 00:10:04,200
What a rare guest.

183
00:10:08,399 --> 00:10:09,320
Been back for so long,

184
00:10:09,320 --> 00:10:10,360
called you so many times,

185
00:10:10,360 --> 00:10:11,039
and you never came.

186
00:10:11,200 --> 00:10:11,960
Why today?

187
00:10:12,279 --> 00:10:13,120
Been busy for a couple of days.

188
00:10:13,120 --> 00:10:14,159
Finally got a chance to see you.

189
00:10:15,240 --> 00:10:15,919
This is my son.

190
00:10:17,200 --> 00:10:17,919
Uncle Lu, can these things

191
00:10:17,919 --> 00:10:19,240
still be used?

192
00:10:19,240 --> 00:10:20,519
If not, I'll sell them as scrap.

193
00:10:20,799 --> 00:10:22,759
You can't find this one anymore.

194
00:10:22,759 --> 00:10:23,799
It's an old model.

195
00:10:24,440 --> 00:10:25,559
Let me introduce you.

196
00:10:27,200 --> 00:10:27,799
This is

197
00:10:28,240 --> 00:10:28,759
A'Xiao.

198
00:10:28,759 --> 00:10:29,360
Lu Xixiao.

199
00:10:29,360 --> 00:10:30,600
The one I always talk about.

200
00:10:31,159 --> 00:10:31,840
Lu Xixiao?

201
00:10:32,840 --> 00:10:33,320
Yeah.

202
00:10:33,600 --> 00:10:34,840
My wife.

203
00:10:35,080 --> 00:10:35,639
Come out.

204
00:10:35,639 --> 00:10:36,480
Don't let anyone hold the baby.

205
00:10:37,200 --> 00:10:37,720
Sit here.

206
00:10:37,720 --> 00:10:38,360
Go play inside.

207
00:10:41,759 --> 00:10:43,799
Come on, rice ball, let me play with you.

208
00:10:44,879 --> 00:10:45,519
What's this?

209
00:10:47,039 --> 00:10:48,320
Throw everything away.

210
00:10:48,399 --> 00:10:49,919
It's been ten years. You can't buy it anymore.

211
00:10:52,399 --> 00:10:53,879
How's it? A lot of changes here, right?

212
00:10:56,519 --> 00:10:57,519
Not much.

213
00:11:03,360 --> 00:11:04,360
Luo He died.

214
00:11:07,840 --> 00:11:08,600
When?

215
00:11:09,759 --> 00:11:10,720
Just a few days ago.

216
00:11:11,440 --> 00:11:12,240
He served a few years in jail.

217
00:11:12,240 --> 00:11:13,919
After he got out, he still didn't get a job.

218
00:11:14,799 --> 00:11:16,279
He drank and gambled every day.

219
00:11:16,279 --> 00:11:17,279
He enjoyed himself every night.

220
00:11:17,720 --> 00:11:18,559
Later, he drank too much

221
00:11:18,559 --> 00:11:19,600
and died.

222
00:11:21,919 --> 00:11:22,519
Do you know

223
00:11:22,519 --> 00:11:23,480
why I'm telling you this?

224
00:11:25,120 --> 00:11:25,759
Why?

225
00:11:26,840 --> 00:11:28,639
You should drink less.

226
00:11:30,240 --> 00:11:30,879
Don't worry.

227
00:11:31,000 --> 00:11:31,960
I don't drink much anyway.

228
00:11:33,679 --> 00:11:34,759
It's been

229
00:11:34,759 --> 00:11:35,559
so many years.

230
00:11:36,919 --> 00:11:37,759
Luo He is dead.

231
00:11:38,720 --> 00:11:39,759
I think some things

232
00:11:39,759 --> 00:11:41,039
should be long gone.

233
00:11:42,320 --> 00:11:43,679
They are long gone.

234
00:11:48,240 --> 00:11:49,519
Do you still like her?

235
00:11:58,720 --> 00:11:59,600
If you like her,

236
00:11:59,600 --> 00:12:00,879
just be nice to her.

237
00:12:01,399 --> 00:12:03,759
Why are you so dramatic?

238
00:12:04,720 --> 00:12:05,720
Is it time

239
00:12:05,720 --> 00:12:06,759
for a happy ending

240
00:12:07,000 --> 00:12:08,320
in the idol drama?

241
00:12:08,399 --> 00:12:09,279
She's living at my house.

242
00:12:10,320 --> 00:12:10,960
What?

243
00:12:12,639 --> 00:12:13,360
What?

244
00:12:15,080 --> 00:12:16,720
You've been back for a long time,

245
00:12:16,720 --> 00:12:17,840
but you never come to see me.

246
00:12:18,159 --> 00:12:19,559
Turns out you have a little stove at home,

247
00:12:19,559 --> 00:12:20,960
sending you warmth secretly.

248
00:12:21,840 --> 00:12:23,320
She stayed at my house for a couple of days.

249
00:12:24,159 --> 00:12:24,879
When she couldn't stay anymore,

250
00:12:24,879 --> 00:12:25,559
she left.

251
00:12:27,440 --> 00:12:28,519
Will there be such a day?

252
00:12:29,000 --> 00:12:32,000
The first love in youth

253
00:12:32,440 --> 00:12:33,320
is not so easy

254
00:12:33,320 --> 00:12:34,200
to forget.

255
00:12:38,320 --> 00:12:39,279
Will there be such a day?

256
00:12:39,279 --> 00:12:39,919
I don't know.

257
00:12:40,879 --> 00:12:42,200
But at least, as long as she is by my side,

258
00:12:43,919 --> 00:12:45,240
I won't feel so bad.

259
00:12:45,919 --> 00:12:46,639
Look at this newspaper.

260
00:12:46,840 --> 00:12:48,240
It's been worn out like this,

261
00:12:48,240 --> 00:12:48,919
but it hasn't been damaged.

262
00:12:49,240 --> 00:12:49,720
I remember

263
00:12:49,720 --> 00:12:51,799
my father kept it

264
00:12:52,440 --> 00:12:53,559
when the building materials factory

265
00:12:53,559 --> 00:12:54,639
he worked for went bankrupt.

266
00:12:54,960 --> 00:12:55,799
It's so dirty.

267
00:12:55,799 --> 00:12:56,720
You still keep it.

268
00:12:58,360 --> 00:13:00,399
It's been 20 years and it hasn't worn out.

269
00:13:06,559 --> 00:13:07,200
Let me see.

270
00:13:10,000 --> 00:13:10,960
It's of good quality.

271
00:13:18,559 --> 00:13:20,000
Look, the wine is spilled on you.

272
00:13:20,679 --> 00:13:21,039
I'm sorry.

273
00:13:21,039 --> 00:13:21,480
Let me wipe it for you.

274
00:13:21,639 --> 00:13:22,639
Let me help you.

275
00:13:22,840 --> 00:13:23,200
I have a spare shirt for you.

276
00:13:23,200 --> 00:13:24,200
I'm sorry.

277
00:13:24,200 --> 00:13:25,320
I can't continue today.

278
00:13:25,480 --> 00:13:26,279
What are you pretending?

279
00:13:26,279 --> 00:13:27,000
Let me go.

280
00:13:36,440 --> 00:13:37,159
Hello, A'Xiao.

281
00:13:37,600 --> 00:13:38,080
Hello.

282
00:13:38,440 --> 00:13:39,840
Can you help me find

283
00:13:39,840 --> 00:13:41,720
a reliable information consulting company?

284
00:13:42,120 --> 00:13:42,879
I need to investigate something.

285
00:13:43,039 --> 00:13:43,600
Well,

286
00:13:44,039 --> 00:13:45,679
you're leaving the art exhibition

287
00:13:45,679 --> 00:13:46,840
to focus on city construction,

288
00:13:47,200 --> 00:13:48,320
and now you're playing the detective,

289
00:13:48,320 --> 00:13:48,799
right?

290
00:13:49,320 --> 00:13:50,600
Just find it for me.

291
00:13:50,600 --> 00:13:51,759
Hurry up and send it to me.

292
00:13:52,399 --> 00:13:53,279
Alright, alright.

293
00:13:53,600 --> 00:13:54,519
You're really something.

